      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start, really hits the atmosphere. can you get a bit more specific with the people in this area? like, what does the crowd look like on these corners? i want to make sure the reader gets a real sense of the types of people who live there or maybe hang out there, to really drive home that feeling of danger and the specific 'vibe' of the community.",
      "source": "evaluator"
